Class MailboxSessionMapperFactory<Id>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.james.mailbox.store.MailboxSessionMapperFactory<Id>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RequestAware, MailboxMapperFactory<Id>, MessageMapperFactory<Id>, SubscriptionMapperFactory
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    HBaseMailboxSessionMapperFactory, InMemoryMailboxSessionMapperFactory, JCRMailboxSessionMapperFactory, JPAMailboxSessionMapperFactory, MaildirMailboxSessionMapperFactory

    public abstract class MailboxSessionMapperFactory<Id>
extends Object
implements RequestAware, MailboxMapperFactory<Id>, MessageMapperFactory<Id>, SubscriptionMapperFactory
    Maintain mapper instances by MailboxSession. So only one mapper instance is used in a MailboxSession
